PE Questions:

Day 0
1.What is the CLI command to get help? /?
2. What is the POSH cmdlet to get help? get-help
3. Which option for the POSH help command shows specific examples on how to use the command? -examples
4. Which of the following will not list the contents of a directory? dir, ls, get-childitem, type
5. Which command will display configuration info about the system? systeminfo
6. Is it possible to switch to PowerShell from CLI? yes 
7. How do I switch from CLI to PowerShell? type PowerShell
8. True or False? Error messages sometimes tell us what is wrong and how to fix it? True
9. Cmdlets in PowerShell follow what naming convention? verb-noun, noun-verb, object-string, string-object
10. How can I edit the contents of a file in CLI? notepad, cd, chdir, move 


